{"id":21,"parent_id":7,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":21,"title":"1 Nephi 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","An angel tells Nephi of the blessings and cursings to fall upon the Gentiles—There are only two churches: the Church of the Lamb of God and the church of the devil—The Saints of God in all nations are persecuted by the great and abominable church—The Apostle John will write concerning the end of the world. About 600–592",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1","order":"05.12.014.1554"},["b","1"],"And it shall come to pass, that if the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Gentiles"],"shall hearken unto the Lamb of God in that day that he shall manifest himself unto them in word, and also in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"power"],", in very deed, unto the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"taking"],"away of their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"stumbling blocks"],"—"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.2","order":"05.12.014.1555"},["b","2"],"And harden not their hearts against the Lamb of God, they shall be numbered among the seed of thy father; yea, they shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"numbered"],"among the house of Israel; and they shall be a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"blessed"],"people upon the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"promised land"],"forever; they shall be no more brought down into captivity; and the house of Israel shall no more be confounded."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.3","order":"05.12.014.1556"},["b","3"],"And that great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"pit"],", which hath been digged for them by that great and abominable church, which was founded by the devil and his children, that he might lead away the souls of men down to hell—yea, that great pit which hath been digged for the destruction of men shall be filled by those who digged it, unto their utter destruction, saith the Lamb of God; not the destruction of the soul, save it be the casting of it into that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"hell"],"which hath no end."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.4","order":"05.12.014.1557"},["b","4"],"For behold, this is according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"captivity"],"of the devil, and also according to the justice of God, upon all those who will work wickedness and abomination before him."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.5","order":"05.12.014.1558"},["b","5"],"And it came to pass that the angel spake unto me, Nephi, saying: Thou hast beheld that if the Gentiles repent it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"well"],"with them; and thou also knowest concerning the covenants of the Lord unto the house of Israel; and thou also hast heard that whoso",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"repenteth"],"not must perish."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.6","order":"05.12.014.1559"},["b","6"],"Therefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"wo"],"be unto the Gentiles if it so be that they harden their hearts against the Lamb of God."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.7","order":"05.12.014.1560"},["b","7"],"For the time cometh, saith the Lamb of God, that I will work a great and a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"marvelous work"],"among the children of men; a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"work"],"which shall be everlasting, either on the one hand or on the other—either to the convincing of them unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"peace"],"and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"life eternal"],", or unto the deliverance of them to the hardness of their hearts and the blindness of their minds unto their being brought down into captivity, and also into destruction, both temporally and spiritually, according to the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"captivity"],"of the devil, of which I have spoken."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.8","order":"05.12.014.1561"},["b","8"],"And it came to pass that when the angel had spoken these words, he said unto me: Rememberest thou the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"covenants"],"of the Father unto the house of Israel? I said unto him, Yea."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.9","order":"05.12.014.1562"},["b","9"],"And it came to pass that he said unto me: Look, and behold that great and abominable church, which is the mother of abominations, whose founder is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.10","order":"05.12.014.1563"},["b","10"],"And he said unto me: Behold there are save",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"two"],"churches only; the one is the church of the Lamb of God, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"other"],"is the church of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"devil"],"; wherefore,",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"whoso"],"belongeth not to the church of the Lamb of God belongeth to that great church, which is the mother of abominations; and she is the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"whore"],"of all the earth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.11","order":"05.12.014.1564"},["b","11"],"And it came to pass that I looked and beheld the whore of all the earth, and she sat upon many",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"waters"],"; and she had dominion over",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"all"],"the earth, among all nations, kindreds, tongues, and people."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.12","order":"05.12.014.1565"},["b","12"],"And it came to pass that I beheld the church of the Lamb of God, and its numbers were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"few"],", because of the wickedness and abominations of the whore who sat upon many waters; nevertheless, I beheld that the church of the Lamb, who were the saints of God, were also upon",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"all"],"the face of the earth; and their dominions upon the face of the earth were small, because of the wickedness of the great whore whom I saw."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.13","order":"05.12.014.1566"},["b","13"],"And it came to pass that I beheld that the great mother of abominations did gather together multitudes upon the face of all the earth, among all the nations of the Gentiles, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"fight"],"against the Lamb of God."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.14","order":"05.12.014.1567"},["b","14"],"And it came to pass that I, Nephi, beheld the power of the Lamb of God, that it descended upon the saints of the church of the Lamb, and upon the covenant people of the Lord, who were scattered upon all the face of the earth; and they were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"armed"],"with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"righteousness"],"and with the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"power"],"of God in great glory."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.15","order":"05.12.014.1568"},["b","15"],"And it came to pass that I beheld that the wrath of God was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"poured"],"out upon that great and abominable church, insomuch that there were wars and rumors of wars among all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"nations"],"and kindreds of the earth."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.16","order":"05.12.014.1569"},["b","16"],"And as there began to be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"wars"],"and rumors of wars among all the nations which belonged to the mother of abominations, the angel spake unto me, saying: Behold, the wrath of God is upon the mother of harlots; and behold, thou seest all these things—"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.17","order":"05.12.014.1570"},["b","17"],"And when the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"day"],"cometh that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"wrath"],"of God is poured out upon the mother of harlots, which is the great and abominable church of all the earth, whose founder is the devil, then, at that day, the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"work"],"of the Father shall commence, in preparing the way for the fulfilling of his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"covenants"],", which he hath made to his people who are of the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.18","order":"05.12.014.1571"},["b","18"],"And it came to pass that the angel spake unto me, saying: Look!"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.19","order":"05.12.014.1572"},["b","19"],"And I looked and beheld a man, and he was dressed in a white robe."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.20","order":"05.12.014.1573"},["b","20"],"And the angel said unto me: Behold",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"one"],"of the twelve apostles of the Lamb."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.21","order":"05.12.014.1574"},["b","21"],"Behold, he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"see"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"write"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"remainder"],"of these things; yea, and also many things which have been."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.22","order":"05.12.014.1575"},["b","22"],"And he shall also write concerning the end of the world."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.23","order":"05.12.014.1576"},["b","23"],"Wherefore, the things which he shall write are just and true; and behold they are written in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"book"],"which thou beheld proceeding out of the mouth of the Jew; and at the time they proceeded out of the mouth of the Jew, or, at the time the book proceeded out of the mouth of the Jew, the things which were written were plain and pure, and most",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"precious"],"and easy to the understanding of all men."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.24","order":"05.12.014.1577"},["b","24"],"And behold, the things which this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"apostle"],"of the Lamb shall write are many things which thou hast seen; and behold, the remainder shalt thou see."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.25","order":"05.12.014.1578"},["b","25"],"But the things which thou shalt see hereafter thou shalt not write; for the Lord God hath ordained the apostle of the Lamb of God that he should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"write"],"them."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.26","order":"05.12.014.1579"},["b","26"],"And also others who have been, to them hath he shown all things, and they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"written"],"them; and they are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"sealed"],"up to come forth in their purity, according to the truth which is in the Lamb, in the own due time of the Lord, unto the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.27","order":"05.12.014.1580"},["b","27"],"And I, Nephi, heard and bear record, that the name of the apostle of the Lamb was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"John"],", according to the word of the angel."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.28","order":"05.12.014.1581"},["b","28"],"And behold, I, Nephi, am forbidden that I should write the remainder of the things which I saw and heard; wherefore the things which I have written sufficeth me; and I have written but a small part of the things which I saw."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.29","order":"05.12.014.1582"},["b","29"],"And I bear record that I saw the things which my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"father"],"saw, and the angel of the Lord did make them known unto me."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.30","order":"05.12.014.1583"},["b","30"],"And now I make an end of speaking concerning the things which I saw while I was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"carried away"],"in the Spirit; and if all the things which I saw are not written, the things which I have written are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"true"],". And thus it is. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1a","order":"05.12.014.1584"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.9.8-9"},"1 Ne. 22:9 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/30.3"},"2 Ne. 30:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.6.6-13"},"3 Ne. 16:6 (6–13)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gentiles"},"TG Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1b","order":"05.12.014.1586"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/1.5"},"1 Thes. 1:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.14"},"1 Ne. 14:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2.2-3"},"Jacob 6:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1c","order":"05.12.014.1588"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.27"},"Ether 12:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1d","order":"05.12.014.1590"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/57.14"},"Isa. 57:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.19"},"Ezek. 7:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.23"},"1 Cor. 1:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.34.29,34"},"1 Ne. 13:34 (29, 34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.20"},"2 Ne. 26:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.2a","order":"05.12.014.1592"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.7.7,29"},"Gal. 3:7 (7, 29)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.18.18-19"},"2 Ne. 10:18 (18–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.13"},"3 Ne. 16:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/21.6.6,22"},"21:6 (6, 22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.10.9-11"},"Abr. 2:10 (9–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.2b","order":"05.12.014.1594"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.12"},"2 Ne. 6:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.10.8-14"},"10:10 (8–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.6.6-7"},"3 Ne. 16:6 (6–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.27"},"20:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.19"},"Morm. 5:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.2c","order":"05.12.014.1596"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-deliverance-of"},"TG Israel, Deliverance of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"Israel, Restoration of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lands-of-inheritance"},"Lands of Inheritance"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.3a","order":"05.12.014.1598"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/57.6"},"Ps. 57:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.2.1-2"},"Matt. 7:2 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.14.13-14"},"1 Ne. 22:14 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.26.25-27"},"D&C 10:26 (25–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.25"},"109:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.3b","order":"05.12.014.1600"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/19.29"},"Alma 19:29"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/damnation"},"TG Damnation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"Hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.4a","order":"05.12.014.1602"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"TG Bondage, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/